question: What are the generic versions of Viagra?
ideal_answer: Generic versions of sildenafil are Elonza, Caverta, Zenegra-100, Vega Asia, Suhagra-100, Vega, Revatio.

snippets.text: The authors conducted a 12-week case series to study the efficacy and safety of Elonza (generic sildenafil) in PAH patients.
